# Nuestro Pulso App

A civic engagement platform for Colombia.

## Features
- Chat
- News
- Surveys
- Community
- Admin

## How to Run

1. Install dependencies:
    ```
    npm install
    ```
2. Start development server:
    ```
    npm run dev
    ```

## How to Deploy (Vercel)
- Build command: `vite build`
- Output directory: `dist`
- Connect your GitHub repo to Vercel

## Folder Structure

```text
src/
  components/
  pages/
  features/
    chat/
    news/
    survey/
    community/
    admin/
public/
```
